Invocation Name: waterfall noise
des: Let the noise of a waterfall lull you to sleep. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Waterfall Noise,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
